I thought this documentary was extremely well done. It's discusses Food, Pharmaceuticals, including vaccines and Govt.  It's not taking sides on the issue, but discussing what happens when profit is the bottom line and when that becomes the most important issue of all.

Includes interviews with a number of prominent scientists and doctors.  This movie is meant to stimulate discussion - some of these issues have gotten so heated that people can't even have rational discussions anymore, which hurts us all.

An excellent, well done documentary that is very relevant for all. Highly recommended!

Such a good piece of work filled with so much information! Lots of documentaries out there that shed light on this or that but this is one that I feel brings it all together. I'm a parent that has tried to avoid gmo's, we don't vaccinate and we just don't generally fall in with the system. It is a bit intimidating when the largest part of your family and friends think you're a nut or a paranoid conspiracy theorist but this has given me the ammunition, I feel, to help them see my point of view. It so thoroughly  lays out facts that could help anyone to see why there are many VALID concerns for those of us who refuse to go along. Rough times in store if we don't change direction soon.
